{"tid":589731,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"【I/A】Brown Dust (3) - 提防假連登公會","createTime":"2018-03-12T05:07:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T05:20:42.000Z","uid":37325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5c0a9fb965033e1024bcaea268c782ca7091efda","tid":589731,"uid":37325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:07:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">韓國 NEOWIZ 3月6日宣佈戰略指令RPG《Brown Dust》（iOS/Android）預定於3月7日正式配信。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195505_47e0b0012668b40f6186d1601bdaf883.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195505_47e0b0012668b40f6186d1601bdaf883.jpg&h=4930ba47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195509_8788c08b0778aae6ff1a0aad46096130.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195509_8788c08b0778aae6ff1a0aad46096130.jpg&h=e2c3f92e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195512_e66449a702abdae8637047bf9e29d66b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195512_e66449a702abdae8637047bf9e29d66b.jpg&h=8ea46a94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195516_7da5ea65940162c195614437c60069d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195516_7da5ea65940162c195614437c60069d3.jpg&h=48b52cd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195525_c9708864050718f395240c097b62ccbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195525_c9708864050718f395240c097b62ccbd.jpg&h=09636aa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195417_7a56d2bff3b5268a5d22dc56ff713f79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195417_7a56d2bff3b5268a5d22dc56ff713f79.jpg&h=40f0c136&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195425_74d2e66348966c75afb1de4dc71a9798.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195425_74d2e66348966c75afb1de4dc71a9798.jpg&h=74ffb367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195425_7e40d6e4c1be56043a2d89f554e7699a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195425_7e40d6e4c1be56043a2d89f554e7699a.jpg&h=00fb64b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195428_df6bffcb857dcc78bb622cb80dabe3df.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195428_df6bffcb857dcc78bb622cb80dabe3df.jpg&h=658c68d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195431_6d6535319addf94d38760631f2d7a5c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195431_6d6535319addf94d38760631f2d7a5c0.jpg&h=ae7b04f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195432_06538f7ef197b7713ba460ec9266003b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195432_06538f7ef197b7713ba460ec9266003b.jpg&h=226e900c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前遊戲的事前登錄人數已突破15萬人，是故已確定遊戲推出後，全部玩家將可獲得相等於一個十連轉蛋份量的600個鑽石以及「☆5傭兵確定券」。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲核心內容是陣營配置，先在戰前佈置我方十體傭兵角色，再在戰鬥階段時接雙方角色的攻勢移動順來互相攻?。作品之內有多達300名角色，而且全都均可提升至最高階級別。<br />\n<br />\nIOS：<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1299021478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Fid1299021478&d=Jd8DbL3f2CtNCvN5tg%2Fm1S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=011c179b\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/jp/app/id1299021478</a><br />\nAN：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.neowizgames.game.browndust.srpg.global\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.neowizgames.game.browndust.srpg.global&d=Jd8DbL3f2CtNCvN5tg%2Fm1S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=03b6a3b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.neowizgames.game.browndust.srpg.global</a><br />\nQooApp：<a href=\"https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/6042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.qoo-app.com%2Fapp%2F6042&d=Jd8DbL3f2CtNCvN5tg%2Fm1S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=d9815964\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.qoo-app.com/app/6042</a></div>"},{"pid":"0f0908c4fad2d5595c5a23e5e2ced7670c85ad95","tid":589731,"uid":37325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T05:08:06.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【照顧絲打/基巴區】</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195804_42f30c25e5fef448db62d7c6c9b6762b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195804_42f30c25e5fef448db62d7c6c9b6762b.jpg&h=d16019f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195807_b0341269fd21723090a3169103438a34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195807_b0341269fd21723090a3169103438a34.jpg&h=9bb96aa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/07/195810_b5fab7dd8a30734ee53ea2a46db8b6be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F07%2F195810_b5fab7dd8a30734ee5